{"tid":522763,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【壞咗點算】拆機專家評分，邊件得零分最難整？","createTime":"2018-01-08T00:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T10:20:26.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e37f40f28f98a181ba1ad0ed1cd1296b0e1478cd","tid":522763,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"知名維修網站iFixit早前公佈5大最難維修裝置，當中微軟佔3部，Apple就佔2部。<br />\n<br />\niFixit每次拆解後會為裝置評分，10分為最易維修，0分則為最難。<br />\n<br />\n2017最矚目的iPhone X獲6分，iFixit評價屏幕及電池延續傳統，容易更換。不過拆解新玻璃機背就較麻煩，壞屏幕後亦要花高價才能換。<br />\n<br />\n賣$38,888高價的iMac Pro，雖然RAM、CPU等都可自行升級，但都只得3分，原因是必須拆開大部分組件才能更換這些可升級的零件。<br />\n<br />\n新iPad雖然只得2分，但已是榜中最易維修。iFixit指新iPad的零件以大量膠水固定，拆開時容易破壞屏幕及保護玻璃。又薄又輕的Macbook雖然轉用標準的螺絲，不過所有零件都焊死在底板，屏幕也沒有保護玻璃容易損壞，所以維修成本較高。<br />\n<br />\n今次贏家就是獲0分的Surface Laptop，iFixit指此機完全沒打算讓人維修，必需鎅破人造麂皮鍵盤才能維修內部零件。除零件被焊死，連電池都難以更換，電池老化後幾乎不能自行更換。"},{"pid":"8c7a611082d9c5ed5e55f6a115de7ad55703a66a","tid":522763,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T00:11:00.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解ifixit個網站最底果度，有支那網站登記既code？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/081047_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F081047_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7b24e054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ifixit.com/smartphone-repairability\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifixit.com%2Fsmartphone-repairability&d=Pr%2FuIvySmj0k7xyqB7RJDxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=23dd8e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ifixit.com/smartphone-repairability</a>"},{"pid":"43d33738af6b172402eecd2b3f7dab7436e7ca20","tid":522763,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T10:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}